Definition: cosmology) the theory that the universe maintains a constant average density with matter created to fill the void left by galaxies that are receding from each other
Example: the steady state theory has been abandoned in favor of the big bang theory
Synonyms: continuous_creation_theory, scientific_theory, cosmology, c, the, theory, that, universe, maintains, a, constant, average, density, with, matter, created, to, fill, void, left, by, galaxies, are, receding, from, each, other, steady, state, has, been, abandoned, in, favor, of, big, bang
Category: noun.cognition
